ActCanadian High Arctic Research Station Act
PrecisAppointment of DAVID SCOTT of Ottawa, Ontario, to be President of the Canadian High Arctic Research Station, to hold office during pleasure, on a full-time basis, for a term of five years, effective August 10, 2015.
